            </div>
            <small class="text-muted">One-click access enabled for all applications</small>
            <div class="mt-2">
              <button class="btn btn-outline-success btn-sm w-100" onclick="testSSO()">
                <i class="bi bi-shield-check me-1"></i>Test SSO
